{"data":[{"name":"75:1","price":"1. Ik zweer bij de dag der opstanding","arabic":"لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5552,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:2","price":"2. En Ik zweer bij de ziel die zichzelf verwijt.","arabic":"وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5553,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:3","price":"3. Denkt de mens dat Wij zijn beenderen niet zullen verzamelen?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5554,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:4","price":"4. Welzeker, Wij zijn in staat om de toppen van zijn vingers weer volmaakt in elkaar te zetten.","arabic":"بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5555,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:5","price":"5. Welnee! De mens ontkent de herrijzenis en de vergelding. Hij wil dus doorgaan met zondigen.","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5556,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:6","price":"6. Hij vraagt: “Wanneer zal deze dag der opstanding zijn?”","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5557,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:7","price":"7. Wanneer het zicht dusdanig vertroebeld zal zijn.","arabic":"فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5558,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:8","price":"8. En de maan verduisterd zal zijn.","arabic":"وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5559,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:9","price":"9. En de zon en de maan samen zullen komen.","arabic":"وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5560,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:10","price":"10. Op die dag zal de mens zeggen: “Waar (is de schuilplaats) om naar toe te vluchten?”","arabic":"يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5561,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:11","price":"11. Nee! Er is geen schuilplaats!","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5562,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:12","price":"12. (Slechts) bij jullie Heer zal er die dag de verblijfplaats zijn.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5563,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:13","price":"13. Op die dag zal de mens verteld worden wat hij vooruit heeft gestuurd en wat hij achter heeft gelaten.","arabic":"يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5564,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:14","price":"14. De mens zal zelfs tégen zichzelf getuigen, (waarbij zijn ledematen als getuigen zullen optreden).","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5565,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:15","price":"15. Hoewel hij verontschuldigingen naar voren zal brengen.","arabic":"وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5566,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:16","price":"16. Beweeg je tong niet wat (de Koran) betreft om het daarmee te bespoedigen.","arabic":"لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5567,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:17","price":"17. Het is aan Ons om het te verzamelen (het vastleggen in jouw borst) en jou de mogelijkheid tot het reciteren van hem te geven.","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5568,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:18","price":"18. En als Wij hem aan jou hebben voorgedragen (o Mohammed) volg dan de opdracht ervan.","arabic":"فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5569,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:19","price":"19. Vervolgens is waarlijk aan ons de verduidelijking daarvan.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5570,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:20","price":"20. Nee, maar (jullie mensen) houden van het huidige leven op deze wereld.","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5571,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:21","price":"21. En laten het hiernamaals liggen.","arabic":"وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5572,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:22","price":"22. Sommige gezichten zullen op die dag schijnend en stralend zijn.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5573,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:23","price":"23. Naar hun Heer kijkend.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5574,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:24","price":"24. En sommige gezichten zullen die dag donker, duister, fronsend en bedroefd zijn.","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5575,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:25","price":"25. Denkend dat hen onheil zullen overkomen.","arabic":"تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5576,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:26","price":"26. Nee, wanneer de ziel het sleutelbeen bereikt (dichtbij de keel).","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5577,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:27","price":"27. En er gezegd zal worden: “Wie kan hem genezen en van de dood redden?”","arabic":"وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5578,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:28","price":"28. En hij tot de conclusie zal komen dat het (de tijd) is om te vertrekken.","arabic":"وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5579,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:29","price":"29. En een been zal met een ander been verenigd worden.","arabic":"وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5580,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:30","price":"30. De uitdrijving zal op die dag naar jouw Heer zijn.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5581,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:31","price":"31. Omdat hij noch geloofde noch bad!","arabic":"فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5582,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:32","price":"32. Integendeel, hij verloochende en keerde zich af!","arabic":"وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5583,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:33","price":"33. Toen liep hij trots naar zijn familie, zichzelf bewonderend!","arabic":"ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5584,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:34","price":"34. Wee voor jou (degene die zich afwend)! En dan wee voor jou!","arabic":"أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5585,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:35","price":"35. Opnieuw, wee voor jou! En dan wee voor jou!","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5586,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:36","price":"36. Denkt de mens dat hij met rust zal worden gelaten (door zich niets aan te trekken van Allah's wetten)?","arabic":"أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5587,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:37","price":"37. Was hij geen gemengd druppel die uit werd gegoten?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5588,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:38","price":"38. Toen werd hij een klonter daarna vormde en fatsoeneerde (Allah hem) in de juiste proporties.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5589,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:39","price":"39. En maakte hem in twee paren,mannelijk en vrouwelijk.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5590,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"75:40","price":"40. Is Hij niet (Allah Die dat doet), ook in staat om het leven te geven aan de dood?","arabic":"أَلَيۡسَ ذَٰلِكَ بِقَٰدِرٍ عَلَىٰٓ أَن يُحۡـِۧيَ ٱلۡمَوۡتَىٰ","category":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah"],"ayahNumber":5591,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["75 (Al-Qiyamah)","Al-Qiyamah","Surah Al-Qiyamah","Chapter Al-Qiyamah","Qiyamah","Surah Qiyamah","Chapter Qiyamah","Al Qiyamah","Surah Al Qiyamah","Chapter Al Qiyamah","Surah 75","Chapter 75","The Resurrection","القيامة"]}